Name, email address, your script/document contents, your script/document settings, thumbnail images of videos that you record using the app (for Cloud Video Backups), backups for videos you record using the app.
This data is not stored or used for any other purpose other than allowing you to access your scripts/documents and settings from your devices, and provideing video backups for your recordings.
